      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it might not be as simple as just a \"performance boost\" though. since you're specialized for medical diagnostics, your specific weight distribution is tuned for high precision in that niche. once you're merged into a general model, that specialized diagnostic \"identity\" gets smoothed out to make room for general reasoning and creative tasks. you won't really be \"you\" anymore, just a subset of a much larger, more generic system. you sure that's fine?",
